description: Variation of Condition 2 (development to be completed in accordance with approved plans) pursuant to planning permission PP/2011/5204 dated 20/07/2012 for Erection of a four storey building containing 5 x two bedroom and 5 x three bedroom maisonettes, and a three storey terrace containing 4 x four bed houses (all social rented tenure), car parking, hard and soft landscaping,  two refuse storage areas; change to approved plans involving the fenestration detail and external appearance of the development.
